    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Walk as Children of Light</strong>&mdash;It is not the will of God that we should be gloomy or impatient, nor that we should be light and trifling. It is Satan&apos;s studied plan to push persons from one extreme to the other. As children of the light, God would have us cultivate a cheerful, happy spirit, that we may show forth the praises of Him who hath called us out of darkness into His marvelous light.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"AUCR 11-1-1904\" data-link=\"498.976\">Australasian Union Conference Record, November 1, 1904</span>.</span></a></sup>",
