    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The mother should cultivate a cheerful, contented, happy disposition. Every effort in this direction will be abundantly repaid in both the physical well-being and <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"433\"></span> the moral character of her children. A cheerful spirit will promote the happiness of her family and in a very great degree improve her own health.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">6<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 374.1\" data-link=\"135.1882\">The Ministry of Healing, 374</span>.</span></a></sup>",
